snippet.title: The Birth of the Dark | Event Trailer
snippet.description:
Sipra, High Priest of the Wishing Shrine is joining you soon with a brand new identity. With her aid, all your wishes in the future are sure to come true. Tap to watch the hero trailer and check out Sipra's new look!


There is another familiar figure in the video. Who might she be...?


New Hero Coming Soon on 05/12
